<br>
Alysia laughed and turned to face him.<br>
&quot;I love it when they beg.&quot; She snarled at him.<br>
<br>
He blinked and looked up. &quot;A woman?&quot; He said with a laugh.<br>
<br>
Alysia smirked widely as she pulled her dagger from her and instead of slitting his throat quickly like she'd normally do, she stabbed it into it. The Roman fell backwards onto his back attemtping to gasp for air.<br>
<br>
She walked back over reaching and pulling her dagger out of the wound. She smiled down at her prey. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center">~*~ Jessica ~*~<br>
